busman 's honeymoon is a 1940 british detective film directed by arthur b. woods . an adaptation of the lord peter wimsey story busman 's honeymoon by dorothy l. sayers , busman 's honeymoon stars robert montgomery , constance cummings , leslie banks , googie withers , robert newton and seymour hicks as mervyn bunter . the plot revolves around newly married famous amateur detective lord peter wimsey ( montgomery ) and his wife , mystery writer harriet vane ( cummings ) , who are looking forward to a quiet honeymoon at their new country cottage when they are reluctantly drawn into the investigation of a local murder . busman 's honeymoon premiered in london in july 1940 and was released in the u.s. as haunted honeymoon in september 1940 .